## Educational Use Notice

This project is created for educational purposes to teach CIP-68 NFT development
on the Cardano blockchain. While the code follows best practices and proven
patterns, users should:

1. Thoroughly test on testnets before mainnet deployment
2. Conduct security audits for production use
3. Understand the implications of smart contract deployment
4. Use appropriate risk management for mainnet operations

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any financial losses or
issues arising from the use of this educational material in production environments.

